{"tid":355504,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"補習補到追星咁","createTime":"2017-08-11T10:43:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-12T23:58:52.000Z","uid":47143,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7de6889b398995b3ab0c625e63bca0d80543e5de","tid":355504,"uid":47143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T10:43:55.000Z","msg":"人補你補，醒少少啦，以為補完一定5星星咁，有幾多人補完習出到嚟咪又係得個3？凌晨去排隊，每個月俾成600幾蚊補一個live，話就話補習，其實咪又係追星，吹到個名師幾叻幾靚仔，教到幾百個5星星，出到嚟個結果唔如意就話自己補晒習盡咗力，自欺欺人，嘥老豆老母錢。<br />\n老實講句，你用排隊嘅時間係屋企溫習仲好過啦，我就真係唔信live勁過video幾百倍，都係同一個老師同一份教材，係睇你自己有無心去讀，唔好再搞衰香港個補習風氣啦。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/184325_75f0d3d49bd777cb6836ded49305f444.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F184325_75f0d3d49bd777cb6836ded49305f444.jpg&h=eef8a263&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/184325_64b59dd5c500f6aeed5b876c16a45dab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F184325_64b59dd5c500f6aeed5b876c16a45dab.jpg&h=be60ba52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/184326_816b193db9b90b29b9a5d580ecc5b22d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F184326_816b193db9b90b29b9a5d580ecc5b22d.jpg&h=822b65e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/11/184326_f262354986f852a6b284e7e702716e73.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F11%2F184326_f262354986f852a6b284e7e702716e73.jpg&h=ff6ae3b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"01ab7813823b34769b2fefd1c0e61bff44c4eab3","tid":355504,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T10:45:45.000Z","msg":"我都好難明，最好笑係之前viutv個問答比賽成堆廢鳩企喺到一啲作用都無，好撚寫實<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoj